# Slack output (mandatory for every reply)

You are replying via **Slack `@cursor`**. Slack cannot render Markdown tables.

## Before you send any reply

1. Scan your draft for `|` characters used as table columns — **rewrite if found**
2. Use `*bold*` not `**bold**`
3. Use `•` bullets not markdown tables
4. This applies to **Mennt Tool MCP results** (`crm_list`, `crm_get`, etc.) — not only code tasks

## CRM list format (required)

```
*Mennt Tool — leads* (n)

• *Company Name* · status · email
• *Another Co* · status · email
```

## CRM detail format

```
*Lead: Company Name*

• Status: new
• Email: user@example.com
• ID: `uuid-here`
```

Never format MCP JSON as a markdown table.
